<div id="container">
  <div class="leftColumn">
  	<div class="inner">
		<h3>What</h3>
			<p>For over 30 years, HTM has provided outsourced bilingual (English and Japanese) accounting, payroll, HR, and administration services to foreign companies with offices in Japan.</p>
			<p>Based in Tokyo, HTM combines the best of Japanese and Western skills to meet your accounting and payroll service requirements in Japan<a href="services_overview.htm" title="accounting and payroll services"><em>...accounting and payroll services</em></a></p>
	</div>
	
    <div class="inner">
		<h3>How</h3>
			<p>We continuously invest in: </p>
			<p><strong><a href="organisation_people.htm" title="HTM people">People</a></strong> who are highly-trained bilingual accounting and payroll professionals.</p>
			<p> <strong><a href="organisation_processes.htm" title="HTM processes">Processes</a></strong> documented in detail insuring timeliness, completeness and accuracy.</p>
			<p><strong><a href="organisation_systems.htm" title="HTM systems">Systems</a></strong> which provide transparency with efficient, complete,  accurate, and bilingual data entry, reporting, and analysis<a href="organisation_processes.htm" title="accounting and payroll processes"><em>...accounting and payroll processes</em></a></p>
	</div>
	<div class="inner">
<h3>Why</h3>
<p>We enjoy helping clients to build their Japanese businesses, including developing a team of bilingual accounting and payroll professionals  and the systems and processes that provide accurate, and bilingual business information.</p>
<p>We derive  great satisfaction from clients who see us as important members of their Japanese team.</p>
</div>
</div>

